// Lab sheet: CV-HP-A3040-001 — protocol-grade gold depth for this SKU
//   (upgraded from a ~98-line page that leaned on SoundGuys MDAQS / battery
//   citations without CairoVolt Timer+ ANC-on/off @50% stopwatches, BT walk,
//   LDAC app verification, or Egypt field ANC notes; vendor "% noise reduction"
//   / any dB figure = vendor-stated or independent-lab citation only, never
//   CairoVolt-measured isolation — §11.3 / §14).
// Wave headphones (over-ear). Physics envelope enforced (§8). §7.5 adapted for
//   over-ear / on-ear: A = full-unit weight (+ hard case); B = playtime AAC
//   ANC OFF + Adaptive ANC ON (+ LDAC differentials); C/E case steps = N/A
//   (no charging case); D/F = USB-C full + quick charge on the unit; G = BT
//   range; H = multipoint (with LDAC exclusivity note); I = ANC qualitative
//   only (no anechoic / no invented dB); J = mic qualitative (no SNR); K =
//   codecs in Soundcore App (LDAC ladder on Android); L = latency qualitative
//   (no ms).
// Sibling ladder: Q20i (A3004, hybrid ANC + soft pouch, no LDAC) → Life Q30
//   (A3028, Transport/Indoor/Outdoor + hard case, no LDAC) → Space One (A3035,
//   Adaptive ANC + LDAC + soft pouch) → Space Q45 (A3040, Adaptive ANC + LDAC
//   + hard case, longer vendor runtime). Sibling files intentionally untouched.
